Supported Discuz!:

* discuz! 6.0.0

Dependency:

* php-curl
* php-twitteroath (bundled, https://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth/)

Install:

* cp -r include/ <discuz-installation-directory>
* cp -r plugins/ <discuz-installation-directory>
* config Twitter OAuth Keys in plugins/twitter/config.php

